Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For centuries the sacred magic{\i0}\N{\i1}of the Divine Crystal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...blessed our world and its people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in time the promise of its power{\i0}\N{\i1}brought war to our lands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lucis, a peaceful kingdom of great magic{\i0}\N{\i1}kept safe by the power of the crystal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Niflheim,{\i0}\N{\i1}a military empire of vast machinery...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...made strong by{\i0}\N{\i1}the might of its Magitek.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Long has war raged between the two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the years passed,{\i0}\N{\i1}Niflheim marched on nearby nations...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...driven by its unsurpassed technology.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To defend itself,{\i0}\N{\i1}Lucis raised a magical wall...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the strength of which comes{\i0}\N{\i1}from the crystal itself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Insomnia alone, the crown city{\i0}\N{\i1}and last bastion of Lucian defense...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...remained beyond Niflheim reach{\i0}\N{\i1}for many years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amid the escalating war...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Prince Noctis of Lucis{\i0}\N{\i1}had come to Tenebrae...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to seek healing for a grievous injury.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He made the long journey{\i0}\N{\i1}together with his father, King Regis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mother, brother, and I,{\i0}\N{\i1}the royalty of Tenebrae...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...had all welcomed their visit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was then that the fires came,{\i0}\N{\i1}everywhere and all at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a mere instant,{\i0}\N{\i1}the whole of Tenebrae was ablaze.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ravus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,General Glauca.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Niflheim attack was an attempt{\i0}\N{\i1}on the lives of the visiting Lucian royalty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,King Regis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunafreya....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From that day until this day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Tenebrae has been gripped{\i0}\N{\i1}in the iron fist of Niflheim...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...sworn enemy of Lucis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Regis assembles a force of mighty{\i0}\N{\i1}warriors to combat the imperial menace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dubbed the Kingsglaive,{\i0}\N{\i1}they fight relentlessly against Niflheim...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...empowered by the magic{\i0}\N{\i1}of their sovereign.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, move to secure the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If they break through, we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the hold-up, Crowe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crowe! Status?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need help. East wall's going down.{\i0}\N{\i1}Pelna, can you get to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucis isn't paying us refugees enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx, I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need support on the east flank.{\i0}\N{\i1}Nyx, where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelna, fall back\Nand regroup with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go easy on the magic, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got people\Nwaiting for you back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worth the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch your back, Libertus.{\i0}\N{\i1}We got more incoming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We ain't gonna last much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Crowe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All Glaives, fall back.{\i0}\N{\i1}Repeat, all Glaives fall back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't take down that daemon.{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm ordering a full retreat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get back here alive.{\i0}\N{\i1}That's an order.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For hearth and home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All units, fall back to the extraction point.{\i0}\N{\i1}Support is inbound.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx! We have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nyx! We have orders!\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Crowe. We gotta move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I ain't got\Nthe stomach for this crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.\NJust like Galahd Canyon back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Libertus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luche, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The imperial forces\Nlook to be withdrawing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I owe you another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it on your tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You just try and get some rest, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You disobeyed a direct order to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For hearth and home, right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I got strength in my body,\NI obey that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fool yourself, Nyx Ulric.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever strength you have\Nis on loan from the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You are nothing without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Await details of your reassignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite their victory all but assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A sudden and inexplicable retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We are at risk nonetheless, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot know\Nwhen they will strike again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, word from the West Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A man claiming to be an envoy\Nof the empire requests an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The envoy from Niflheim awaits without,\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well met, my dear Lucians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Niflheim grown so bold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...that they send the chancellor himself\Nas envoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And under no guard, at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an honor to be recognized\Nby the great King Regis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet permit me to stand on ceremony\Nand introduce myself nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ardyn Izunia, Chancellor of Niflheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...at your humble service.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I come to you on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...most auspicious of days\Nto offer terms of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As you no doubt surmised...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...that recent maneuver of ours\Nwas no strategic retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...a gesture of imperial goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you, we wish nothing more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...than to bring a swift end\Nto this senseless war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And we require\Nbut a singular compliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your grand Insomnia here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucis must forfeit\Nall territories to Niflheim rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Insomnia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The jewel in the crown\Nof the Lucian kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish of me to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is just one more trivial thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It concerns your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The fetching Prince Noctis of Lucis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the fair Princess Lunafreya\Nof Tenebrae....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They are to be wed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem vexed, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure you, the princess\Nstill holds you in the highest regard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...as she has done\Nall these 12 long years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know if anyone's told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we don't take kindly\Nto insubordination around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do yourself a favor, take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what a hundred years of peace\Nlooks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lasting peace made by the Wall\Nand the Wall alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we don't need any of you\Nimmigrants...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...jumping around, playing war hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NRough day on the gate, huh, Glaive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk.\NIt's your fault he got stuck there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Not a very nice welcome for a big hero.\N-Not a very nice outfit for one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it brings out my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you put in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes like a chocobo turd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shut your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't Galahd.\NThat's the way folks around here like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. I'm glad to see you're willing to\Nsell out our heritage for a few extra gil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Libertus.\NYou thank Nyx for saving your life yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Crowe.\NNyx and I are too close for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He helps me, I help him.\NThat's the way it's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got a little help\Nfrom something else, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I need all I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For hearth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-And home.\N-And home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Nyx the Gatekeeper.\NHow's the new post treating you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's amazing.\NYou guys would love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate watch are real sweethearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know they hate us outsiders\Nmore than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So bored they got nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Boredom's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Means there's peace, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd fight a hundred more wars\Nfor Galahdans to know boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't go dying yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I still owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would the Glaive be\Nwithout its hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you not talk like this\Nwhile we're drinking, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We just sent the Niffs running\Nwith tails between their legs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't running from us.\NNo, they were toying with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being such a buzzkill, Luche.\NWe all know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know they sent an envoy\Nto the Citadel after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What for? To offer their surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-More like demand ours.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Demand? My ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The empire's got Lucis on its last legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect time to make demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are losing this war, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucis cannot rely\Non the Kingsglaive alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Accepting the truce may be\Nour best course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak of matters\Nbeyond the New Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no need of a truce here,\Nso long as it stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And if our position worsens,\Nwe still have the Old Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but this truce\Nwill end the fighting altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could compromise--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Compromise is unwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We know nothing\Nof Niflheim's true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not fool yourselves.\NThe Walls are far from impenetrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The paths left to us are few.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Wall draws its power\Nfrom the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am able to sustain it for some years yet,\Nif the kingdom requires it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But the chancellor spoke one truth,\Nif only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We are old, and the Old Wall....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot command the Old Wall\Nwith a weakened hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...nor do I have the strength to muster\Nan offensive to turn the tide on this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let the choice be made,\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Help Mother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you never\Nlose your lunch like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this ancient art,\Nsecret of the royal family and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Libertus! Nyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, guys, you gotta see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things were hectic in the capital today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...as the Lucian government{\i0}\N{\i1}announced full acceptance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...of what some are criticizing{\i0}\N{\i1}as the unilateral peace terms...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...proposed by Chancellor Izunia{\i0}\N{\i1}of Niflheim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The signing of the truce will see{\i0}\N{\i1}power over all Lucian territories...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...transferred to the empire,{\i0}\N{\i1}with the sole exception of Insomnia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In return, Niflheim guarantees{\i0}\N{\i1}the safety of Insomnia and its citizenry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...as well as a cessation{\i0}\N{\i1}to all hostilities...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...bringing a decisive end{\i0}\N{\i1}to this long and bitter war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All that fighting we did.\NAll for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Glaives.\NAssemble in the briefing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The king has spoken,\Nand you have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All lands beyond the Wall\Nare to be relinquished to the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Will no regions be spared?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-None.\N-But your home's out there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the king do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.43,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it'll end this damn war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Crowe.\N-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to deploy.\NYou're being sent to infiltrate Tenebrae.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenebrae, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission details are classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Report to my office for briefing\Nin 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And, Nyx....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're off the West Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been reassigned\Nto the castle guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what you were\Ntalking about, Luche?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:22:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-This wasn't our decision to make.\N-Not ours to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are our homes out there!\NOur people!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just gonna go along\Nand abandon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't go along with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...the empire will unleash all hell\Non Insomnia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-We'll unleash it right back at them!\N-Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nothing to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.39,0:23:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats, snuck in from beyond the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, they had a use for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.87,0:23:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...when they realized\Nwe could work their magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So they handpicked us\Nfrom all the other rats out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...and just let us nibble away\Nat his royal majesty's precious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But as soon as this war's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's back to the sewers for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you too, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You missing home so much, Libertus,\Nwhy don't you and Nyx head on back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Niflheim will welcome you\Nwith open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a home out there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said sentiment amongst the people\Nis favorable, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.22,0:24:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Most all will welcome this peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you yourself\Nhave not heard their voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.56,0:24:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...how can you claim\Nto know their hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What of the mission to Tenebrae,\NYour Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.17,0:24:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is such clandestine action wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.74,0:24:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If discovered, it will only serve\Nto provoke the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The empire remains our enemy\Nuntil the treaty is signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as we are at war...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.78,0:24:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...His Majesty intends to remain\None step ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.18,0:24:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.63,0:25:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A hairpin? I didn't think you were\Ninto that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.66,0:25:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for me.\NIt's a gift for the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But keep that quiet.\NNobody's supposed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.87,0:25:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.17,0:25:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your back out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.24,0:25:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're sick of hearing it,\Nbut you're like a little--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.18,0:25:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Little sister to you.\NYeah, I am sick of hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.55,0:25:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you come back\Nin one piece, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.99,0:25:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Says the guy in two pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.05,0:25:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Lunafreya,\NI have left the rear gate open.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.02,0:26:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Must you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.19,0:26:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.86,0:26:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.90,0:26:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not recall granting you permission to\Nleave your quarters, Lunafreya.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.94,0:26:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ravus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not to leave this room again\Nuntil the journey to Lucis.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.85,0:26:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.62,0:26:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My own good?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.32,0:26:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is truly going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.62,0:26:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What cause does the empire have\Nto see me wed to Noctis?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.76,0:26:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They have offered a peace,\Nand your marriage is the olive branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.30,0:26:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.60,0:26:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What you believe does not concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.87,0:26:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What does concern me\Nis you sneaking off...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.10,0:26:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...to go tell our mother's killer\Nabout some plot you've dreamt up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.61,0:26:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are wrong to hate King Regis.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.68,0:26:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Niflheim killed Mother, not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.65,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They murdered her\Nand made you their lapdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.17,0:27:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.81,0:28:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An air of jubilation has swept the city{\i0}\N{\i1}in anticipation of the coming armistice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.71,0:28:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With only three days remaining until{\i0}\N{\i1}the peace is officially signed into effect...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.15,0:28:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...throngs of citizens{\i0}\N{\i1}have taken to the streets to show....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.30,0:28:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lucis needs your strength,{\i0}\N{\i1}young warriors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.00,0:28:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't need{\i0}\N{\i1}any of you immigrants.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.80,0:28:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever strength you have{\i0}\N{\i1}is on loan from the king.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.87,0:28:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-You are nothing without him.{\i0}\N{\i1}-Nyx, help Mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Selena, get down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.48,0:28:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}--and the waves of{\i0}\N{\i1}imperial diplomats entering the city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.32,0:28:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess? Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.15,0:28:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.09,0:28:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She was amongst the last of\Nthe imperial contingent to enter the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.25,0:29:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.32,0:29:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reporting to my post now though, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.29,0:29:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,New orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.12,0:29:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.\NWe've got a princess to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.23,0:29:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice ride, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.40,0:29:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We've taken him outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.54,0:29:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he have a wedding to plan, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.81,0:29:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the "sir" crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.05,0:29:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The king has a plan of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.15,0:29:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Noctis and Princess Lunafreya\Nare to meet far from Insomnia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.22,0:29:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing here then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.39,0:29:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Complicating things.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.22,0:30:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We sent Crowe to find the princess\Nand escort her out of Tenebrae.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.30,0:30:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still trying to figure out\Nwhat went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.21,0:30:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know what you think about this war,\Nbut what do you think about this peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.45,0:30:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You happy giving up your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.92,0:30:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the king's decision.\NI owe him for taking me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.23,0:30:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lucky.\NThere are people in Galahd who weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.03,0:30:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And they need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.43,0:30:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.97,0:30:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What good will you be\Nwithout the king's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.14,0:30:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, always wanting to save somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.88,0:30:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. Believe me.\NBut it doesn't win wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.48,0:30:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just wanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.22,0:30:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.55,0:31:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Libertus is the one\Nyou need to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.92,0:31:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll go back if things gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.89,0:31:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst is yet to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.45,0:31:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea\Nwho you're stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.95,0:31:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this gate now,\Nand maybe you'll have a job tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.99,0:31:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-King's orders.\N-Are you sure you want to risk...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.59,0:31:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...a diplomatic issue now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.53,0:31:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the personal escort\Nof Lady Lunafreya Nox Fleuret...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.07,0:31:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...princess of the former Tenebrae and--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.57,0:31:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And our kingdom's beloved bride-to-be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.60,0:31:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to sovereign jurisdiction.\NWe'll take care of things from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.67,0:31:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Forgive me, Captain Drautos.\N-See Her Highness to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.38,0:32:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that you--\NI wasn't made aware of any--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.68,0:32:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me. Thank you.\N-No, you-- I must--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.05,0:32:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I must-- No, I have to clear it\Nwith my superiors first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.15,0:32:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.30,0:32:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Royal Highness,\NPrincess Lunafreya of Tenebrae.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.64,0:32:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a long time, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.61,0:32:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.05,0:32:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.55,0:32:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Noctis isn't here, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.16,0:32:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my dear. He is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.03,0:32:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too old to fight this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.30,0:32:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to receive the empire\Nand accept their treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.97,0:32:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.47,0:33:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had hoped to hold the wedding\Nelsewhere, somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.28,0:33:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent one of my Glaive\Nto see you there, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.18,0:33:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.59,0:33:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ready an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.29,0:33:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go to my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.69,0:33:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.56,0:33:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever I go, the empire will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.66,0:33:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It would only place the prince\Nin greater danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.34,0:33:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my duty to protect the prince\Nand see his destiny fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.31,0:33:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These 12 years\Nhave not changed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.15,0:33:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And what of your destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.75,0:33:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My duty is my destiny, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.62,0:33:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to accept\Nwhatever may come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.23,0:34:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.77,0:34:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All these lands will be imperial soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.07,0:34:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Reckon things will get better\Nwhen them Niffs start calling the shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.38,0:34:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one damn bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.24,0:34:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't matter who's calling the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.45,0:34:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Long as they're calling them\Nfrom behind the Wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.51,0:34:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...ain't nothing gonna change\Naround here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.15,0:34:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.52,0:34:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.79,0:34:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.60,0:34:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust the reunion was a happy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.73,0:34:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she been a hostage of Niflheim\Nall this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.54,0:34:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a symbol of the peace.\NThat's all I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.74,0:34:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't sound like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.07,0:34:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like she's here\Nfor something much bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.18,0:34:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your orders are to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.08,0:34:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to look, not to listen, not to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.68,0:34:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.48,0:34:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drautos.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.75,0:34:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.46,0:35:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the hell out of my way.\NThat's my friend you got in there, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.70,0:35:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you can't go in\Nuntil the examination has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.76,0:35:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What examination?\NWhat the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.10,0:35:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take it easy, big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.54,0:35:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These bastards rushed Crowe in there\Nthe moment she got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.87,0:35:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they won't let me in\Nto see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.18,0:35:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.38,0:35:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Crowe's personal effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.29,0:36:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do with them as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.46,0:36:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what kind of mission\Ndid you really send her on?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.63,0:36:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No Glaive winds up dead\Non a standard escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.80,0:36:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see the armistice does not interfere\Nwith a full investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.17,0:36:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a good soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.74,0:36:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Her death will not go unanswered.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.72,0:36:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What a life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.49,0:36:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She was brought up an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.56,0:36:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Run out of her village.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.80,0:36:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember the first time I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.90,0:36:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrawny little thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.24,0:36:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...all covered in dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.74,0:36:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a friend in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.38,0:37:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But those eyes....
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.48,0:37:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.35,0:37:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something\Nabout those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.29,0:37:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She deserved better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.50,0:37:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would've done anything\Nto give it to--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.95,0:37:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Libertus, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.59,0:37:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Crowe died a Glaive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.02,0:37:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still honor her\Nby fighting as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.43,0:37:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dumber than me sometimes,\Nyou know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.63,0:37:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.80,0:37:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucis killed Crowe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.57,0:38:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.74,0:38:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the king there's no peace to be had\Nfrom throwing the weak to the wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.72,0:38:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight my own fight from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.65,0:38:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.35,0:38:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hairpin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.62,0:38:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't think you were{\i0}\N{\i1}into that kind of thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.69,0:38:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not for me.{\i0}\N{\i1}It's a gift for the princess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.00,0:39:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A most grand reception, King Regis.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.97,0:39:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You honor all of Niflheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.10,0:39:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the honor is ours,\NEmperor Aldercapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.41,0:39:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have ventured far\Nto grace us with your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.55,0:39:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the very least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.72,0:39:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be an historic day\Nfor both our nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.05,0:39:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And your Insomnia is truly a marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.39,0:40:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My own cities pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray we are able to take away much\Nfrom this visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.87,0:40:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.58,0:40:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am afraid we were never\Nproperly introduced yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.88,0:40:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it's going to have to wait,\NYour Highness. I'm on guard duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.85,0:40:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then surely there's\Nno safer place for me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.72,0:40:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.19,0:40:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx. Nyx Ulric.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.47,0:40:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something else\NI wish to ask you, Nyx Ulric.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.04,0:40:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,King Regis said he sent\None of your order to come find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.54,0:40:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I should like to offer my thanks in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.78,0:40:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where might I find this brave soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.09,0:41:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I did not--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.96,0:41:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-I am so sorry.\N-Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.66,0:41:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.00,0:41:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She was carrying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.04,0:41:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was meant for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.17,0:41:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.64,0:41:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.58,0:41:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She would've wanted you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.78,0:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will carry it with me always.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.62,0:41:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.75,0:42:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea\Nwhat this peace means?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.95,0:42:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It means our homes are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.55,0:42:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.99,0:42:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.20,0:42:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard I could find\Nsome treaty haters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.87,0:42:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I come to the right place?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.13,0:42:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly have.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.04,0:42:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone say hello to a man\Nwho spends his days...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.61,0:42:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the loyal service of our good king.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.81,0:42:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Spent."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.14,0:42:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Those days are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.95,0:42:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done listening\Nto that bastard's lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.65,0:42:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He may sit on a throne,\Nbut he ain't no king...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.32,0:42:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...least not of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.95,0:42:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.19,0:42:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...welcome to the resistance, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.73,0:42:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're here to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.06,0:42:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.24,0:43:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.97,0:43:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...wherever Noctis is, keep him safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.91,0:43:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.81,0:43:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To what god do you pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.12,0:43:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You, the slave of fate and destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.29,0:43:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon your prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.86,0:43:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods do not listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,General Glauca. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.89,0:43:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are far too clever\Nto have ever believed in this peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.33,0:43:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pity you couldn't see your beloved Noctis.\NYou have another purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.17,0:43:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not here for Niflheim.\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.07,0:43:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.81,0:43:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.94,0:43:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.61,0:43:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come tomorrow, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.36,0:44:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niflheim contingent has left the hotel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.70,0:44:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Less than three hours{\i0}\N{\i1}until the ceremony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.03,0:44:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bolster the Citadel guard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.91,0:44:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nyx, is the princess with you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.88,0:44:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.01,0:44:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on duty at the Citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.91,0:44:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, the Niffs just left{\i0}\N{\i1}for the ceremony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.15,0:44:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And she wasn't with them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.27,0:45:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-A homing beacon?{\i0}\N-Yeah, I'll send the coordinates now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.88,0:45:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you pinpoint a location for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.38,0:45:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure, but it sounds like{\i0}\N{\i1}a wild-goose chase.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.91,0:45:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guess you got some{\i0}\N{\i1}free time on your hands, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.85,0:45:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I do, for better or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.11,0:45:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those coordinates are about{\i0}\N{\i1}20 miles south of Insomnia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.01,0:45:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.81,0:45:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell was Crowe doing{\i0}\N{\i1}all the way out there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.82,0:45:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. They sent her to--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.92,0:46:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I need another favor, Pelna.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.32,0:46:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull those coordinates up on the radar\Nand let me know what you find.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.39,0:46:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On it. You're thinking{\i0}\N{\i1}this is all a big deal now, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.36,0:46:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, too big to ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.76,0:46:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me, sir. Excuse me.\N-Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.00,0:46:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Whoa, wait a minute.\N-Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.77,0:46:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up. This is not the gate watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.81,0:46:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the heart of our city,\Nthe home of our king.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.91,0:46:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony must not be disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.78,0:46:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutralize any threat quickly and quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.39,0:46:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.06,0:46:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.47,0:47:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Glaive to command.\NAre you there, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.54,0:47:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.14,0:47:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, Drautos.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.94,0:47:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jackpot, Nyx. There's a whole fleet of{\i0}\N{\i1}airships sitting at that spot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.18,0:47:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Niflheim.\N{\i1}-Yup, and from the looks of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.32,0:47:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I'd say they're headed to war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.12,0:47:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's the captain?\N{\i1}-Should be at the Citadel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.52,0:47:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no answer on his frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.09,0:47:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know, must have his hands full{\i0}\N{\i1}with the escort detail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.42,0:47:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelna, one last favor.\NI need you to prep the Glaive for action.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.19,0:47:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.46,0:47:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You wanna deploy{\i0}\N{\i1}without the captain's order?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.40,0:47:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me. Just get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.96,0:47:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, what am I supposed to tell--?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.90,0:47:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down, Glaive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.54,0:48:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony is in less than two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.98,0:48:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We must make ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.31,0:48:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.28,0:48:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.58,0:48:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A man of the Kingsglaive is here, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.59,0:48:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He demands an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.29,0:48:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Demands"?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.22,0:48:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your Majesty, please.\N-Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.66,0:48:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the order to deploy the Glaive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.43,0:48:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.03,0:48:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A Niflheim fleet makes ready for war\N20 miles to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.97,0:48:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An imperial fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.97,0:48:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.17,0:48:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarus, post guards\Noutside the treaty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.37,0:48:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be seen\Nas a lack of faith in the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.41,0:48:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which we all harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.48,0:48:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.58,0:48:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We may well have to take\NEmperor Aldercapt into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.35,0:48:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Detain him?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.12,0:48:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That would go beyond\Na new declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.49,0:48:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are still at war, Clarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.22,0:48:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Nyx Ulric.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.93,0:48:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How soon can the Kingsglaive deploy?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.30,0:49:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On your word, at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.10,0:49:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.07,0:49:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Save Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.58,0:49:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What if this is a diversion?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.51,0:49:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.05,0:49:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenebrae's princess is onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.65,0:49:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got two jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.32,0:49:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.26,0:49:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And stop those Niff ships\Nfrom flying on Insomnia.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.24,0:49:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We go in teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.67,0:49:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Standard infiltrate and extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.31,0:49:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx, you command. We'll follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.65,0:49:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Glaive stands together,\Ncaptain or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.38,0:49:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For hearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.55,0:49:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And home!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.43,0:50:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are less than 20 minutes away{\i0}\N{\i1}from the signing of this historic treaty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.18,0:50:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I received word{\i0}\N{\i1}of the king's order to deploy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.28,0:50:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll see to matters in the city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.75,0:50:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have your mission,{\i0}\N{\i1}and it won't be easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.09,0:50:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The objective is two-fold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.56,0:50:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Secure the hostage,{\i0}\N{\i1}and stay the enemy advance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.16,0:50:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.33,0:50:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Glaive already died{\i0}\N{\i1}for this princess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.76,0:50:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niflheim won't give her up easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.68,0:50:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Team Two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.17,0:51:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.53,0:51:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry up, Nyx!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.34,0:51:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.86,0:51:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.26,0:51:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparing to head below deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.83,0:51:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do not engage the enemy{\i0}\N{\i1}until instructed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.70,0:51:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ceremony is underway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.37,0:51:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's wait and see{\i0}\N{\i1}how Niflheim plays this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.28,0:51:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kingsglaive\Nhave infiltrated the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.44,0:52:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything's going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.71,0:52:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulric reporting. Six Niflheim airships\Nconfirmed inbound for Insomnia.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.75,0:52:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx, this doesn't feel like a war fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.81,0:53:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might've found her.\NI got a guarded door here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.92,0:53:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two Niff MTs. What's the plan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.62,0:53:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold position.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.69,0:53:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrived at destination.\NHigh possibility of target in the vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.26,0:53:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proceed to secure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.63,0:53:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to mean a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.27,0:53:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep it quiet and keep it confined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.87,0:53:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelna, you're clear to engage.\NBut keep it quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.31,0:53:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.58,0:53:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive my delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.38,0:53:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit of unforeseen trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.75,0:53:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing too vexing, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.92,0:53:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple theft, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.72,0:53:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A daring thief, to steal from the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.83,0:54:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps magical walls and castle gates\Ndo not keep all things safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.70,0:54:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.70,0:54:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter. That which was taken\Nwill soon be returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.71,0:54:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.77,0:54:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a paragon of kingly composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.48,0:54:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.82,0:54:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...how can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.25,0:54:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this thing is no mere trinket.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.02,0:54:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It possesses a will all its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.39,0:54:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to break any thief's grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.53,0:54:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds a very fine prize indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.94,0:54:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.35,0:54:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For me? You shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.05,0:54:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Target confirmed. She's unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.76,0:55:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Glaives have recovered the princess,\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.87,0:55:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you found your thief?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.47,0:55:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.91,0:55:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was stolen remains intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.71,0:55:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Joyous news.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.38,0:55:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am relieved to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.68,0:55:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.62,0:55:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...how heavy a sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.98,0:55:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...does the crime of theft\Ncarry in your empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.35,0:55:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the heaviest.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.76,0:55:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Although there is one...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.76,0:55:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.93,0:55:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are about to get ugly over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.46,0:55:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelna, get out of there. It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.40,0:55:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is that?\N-A curious old law...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.87,0:55:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...I still permit in the outlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.71,0:55:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A thief who escapes his captor...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.74,0:55:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...can no longer be held to account\Nfor his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.88,0:55:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A warning to the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.05,0:56:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Never show weakness,\Nlest you forgo the hand of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.65,0:56:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, good king.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.92,0:56:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Far from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.39,0:56:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The treaty is now on the table.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.46,0:56:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The countdown begins{\i0}\N{\i1}to this historical moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.06,0:56:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is a warning{\i0}\N{\i1}to the hand of justice itself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.84,0:56:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...never to loose its grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.82,0:56:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit One, secure the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.85,0:56:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit Two, stand your ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.56,0:56:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelna.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.16,0:56:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One Tenebrae princess, safe and--
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.43,0:56:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.46,0:57:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The crystal. They're after the crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.17,0:57:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something going on below deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.00,0:57:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's not going to make it\Nto Insom--
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.01,0:57:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You....
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.95,0:57:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.58,0:57:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Insomnia is under attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.65,0:57:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.89,0:57:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-General Glauca.\N-You were bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.12,0:57:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Us coming here was all part of their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.62,0:58:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Target secured.\NRequest permission to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.73,0:58:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Granted. Get to--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.22,0:58:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The crystal will not serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.79,0:58:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor you...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.96,0:58:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...once I take it from this accursed city.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.79,0:58:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the crystal I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.86,0:58:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wall. It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.04,0:59:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back. It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.58,0:59:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.32,0:59:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.83,0:59:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got into you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.96,1:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, we must escape while we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.43,1:02:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Clarus.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.40,1:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear escape is no longer an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.74,1:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,General Glauca.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.82,1:02:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it up? Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.34,1:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Luche!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.02,1:03:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.96,1:03:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.80,1:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They teach piloting\Nback at the royal academy?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.30,1:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.01,1:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a long time\Nsince I fought at your side, old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.85,1:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.35,1:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...but this time it is not your fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.28,1:03:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to leave, go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.19,1:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And abandon my king? I think not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.52,1:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, our magic is bound to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.53,1:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fall, Lucis falls.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.86,1:04:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us once more into the fray...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.23,1:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.49,1:04:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take me back to King Regis.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.96,1:04:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?\NInsomnia's a war zone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.13,1:04:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty. I cannot neglect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.87,1:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, I heard all that before.\N-Then you know we must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.24,1:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry to do what? Get yourself killed?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.27,1:04:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not fear death.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.41,1:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with all this brave princess act.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.22,1:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pray this thing will make the trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.44,1:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarus.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.61,1:05:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I daresay everything has proceeded\Naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.49,1:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-No?\N-So it has.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.55,1:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have broken the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.42,1:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is to break the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.03,1:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take our leave, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.40,1:05:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun will soon set.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.60,1:05:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We need not be here\Nto witness the terrors of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.28,1:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The crystal.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.35,1:06:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going too fast.\NWe have to land.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.19,1:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're gonna have to give me a minute.\N-There is no time. I will go on my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.29,1:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You got wings underneath that dress?\NYou can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.63,1:06:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all miracles are made by magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.67,1:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not fear death.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.57,1:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What I fear is doing nothing\Nand losing everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.74,1:06:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.08,1:06:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can thank magic for that miracle,\NYour Highness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.14,1:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The reckoning is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.68,1:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dawn of a new age.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.65,1:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the crystal.\NWhat more would you take from me?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.40,1:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ring of the Lucii.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.24,1:07:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost my mother, my country,{\i0}\N{\i1}my birth-right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.38,1:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Niflheim was the only life left to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.58,1:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of that was for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.78,1:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The ring belongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.73,1:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me, Lucian kings of old,\Nfor I am Ravus Nox Fleuret...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.80,1:07:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...and none is more worthy of your power\Nthan I.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.10,1:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.51,1:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you refuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.60,1:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.69,1:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, through here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.48,1:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This leads to a hidden passageway.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.71,1:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.88,1:09:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you are away, make for Altissia.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.78,1:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctis awaits you there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.89,1:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your Majesty.\N-You knew this was coming--
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.39,1:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But it was the only way\Nto draw their wrath from Noctis.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.93,1:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the way of our king?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.43,1:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice Lucian sons to save his own?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.73,1:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To save the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.90,1:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See Luna safely to Altissia.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.71,1:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not an order\Nfrom a king to his Glaive.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.54,1:09:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a plea from one man to another.\NPlease, Nyx Ulric, keep her safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.28,1:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For the future of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.95,1:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.79,1:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.72,1:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.29,1:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time it passed to another's keeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.33,1:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.60,1:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get back.\N-Please. Don't leave us.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.50,1:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your mother\Nwould wish the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.80,1:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That you and Noctis live happily.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.57,1:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All those years captive\Nbecause I failed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.71,1:10:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.88,1:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Locked doors\Nwill seal your fate no longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.91,1:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,King Regis....
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.58,1:11:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hope goes with you now,\NNyx Ulric. Godspeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.02,1:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the King of Lucis...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.73,1:11:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...who hoarded tranquility\Nwithin his precious walls.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.40,1:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your tranquility now, king?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.47,1:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is your peace,\Nby steel's swift descent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.52,1:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.04,1:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We must get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.68,1:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what your king wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.39,1:13:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Lunafreya has escaped{\i0}\N{\i1}with the ring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.76,1:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find her at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.96,1:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is not to leave the city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.80,1:13:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ulric to command. Come in, captain.\N{\i1}-Footage of the perpetrators...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.77,1:13:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...was captured{\i0}\N{\i1}by a nearby surveillance camera.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.90,1:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here are images of the six suspects.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.80,1:13:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One has been identified{\i0}\N{\i1}as Galahdian refugee, Libertus Ostium...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.04,1:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...a former member{\i0}\N{\i1}of the Lucian Kingsglaive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.58,1:13:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.62,1:13:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you, I got you. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.75,1:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.09,1:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.76,1:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.56,1:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're free now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.06,1:13:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're free? What do you mean,\N"We're free"?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.16,1:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The empire. They promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.93,1:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This district's ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.00,1:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All the refugees.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.73,1:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our new home.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.10,1:14:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-The empire? You went in with Niflheim?\N-Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.17,1:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this. Meet up with the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.58,1:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the hero of our revolution, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.82,1:14:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.46,1:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy just doesn't know\Nwhen he's beat.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.80,1:14:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can you drive?\N-I can try.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.17,1:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.72,1:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No warping for you this time, hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.83,1:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the wheel. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.73,1:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are without your magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.17,1:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You noticed that, huh?\NIt must have died with the king.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.20,1:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a mess of my city, Glaive.\NI thought I told you not to go playing hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.01,1:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the ship to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.78,1:15:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got a royal fare to see to.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.73,1:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.25,1:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not all miracles\Nare made by magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.13,1:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.85,1:17:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell did you do\Nto piss these things off?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.02,1:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me they're after.\NIt's the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.96,1:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so special about this ring?\NDon't tell me the future's riding on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.66,1:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He who wears the ring\Ncommunes with the Lucii...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.63,1:17:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-...and commands great power.\N-What kind of power?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.03,1:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A forbidden one.\NSealed within the ring, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.70,1:17:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Old Wall.\NI thought that was just a bedtime story.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.72,1:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can assure you it is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.22,1:17:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Lucii grant their power\Nonly to those they deem worthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.65,1:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So that guy who tried it on back there...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.89,1:17:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...I guess he wasn't deemed worthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.23,1:17:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.30,1:17:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,These 12 years have changed Ravus.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.80,1:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He is bound by the past,\Nand lost in his lust for power.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.80,1:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did they find us?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.03,1:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hairpin. They're tracking it.\NGive it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.14,1:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a little sister once.\NShe was killed when the empire came.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.11,1:18:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't save her.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.84,1:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was as helpless then as I am now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.28,1:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't show her the future\Nshe wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.15,1:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,True power is not something that is found\Nby those who seek it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.23,1:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is something that comes\Nto those who deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.50,1:19:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister wanted you to see\Na future as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.97,1:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would wish the same\Nfor family they love.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.08,1:19:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't pull any punches, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.49,1:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.32,1:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you hear me?{\i0}\N{\i1}Repeat, this is Drautos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.52,1:19:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you hear me? Over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.23,1:19:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your timing's impeccable, captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.83,1:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Lucii are real...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.47,1:19:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...they sure don't seem to mind\Ntheir city getting torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.34,1:19:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're to rendezvous and regroup.{\i0}\N{\i1}Understood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.02,1:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Might not be so easy, captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.92,1:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My wings have been clipped,\Nif you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.35,1:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ulric. Are you all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.59,1:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead, if that's what you mean, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.43,1:20:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Head for Section D{\i0}\N{\i1}as soon as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.90,1:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have an evacuation team ready.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.53,1:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suppose you could meet me\Nat the gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.27,1:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd kind of like to\Nget the hell out of this city.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.87,1:20:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imperials hold all exits.{\i0}\N{\i1}There's no way through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.54,1:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll meet you at Section D.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.07,1:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cut all radio contact until then.{\i0}\N{\i1}And make sure you get there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.24,1:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a date, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.10,1:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.53,1:21:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Status report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.10,1:21:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ulric killed some good men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.24,1:21:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-What about the ring?{\i0}\N{\i1}-We don't have it yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.87,1:21:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Glauca. King Regis is dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.27,1:21:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ring is on its way to Section D.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.01,1:21:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must recover the ring{\i0}\N{\i1}to realize our goal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.58,1:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Ulric or the princess get in the way,{\i0}\N{\i1}take them out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.58,1:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reclaim our hearth and home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.15,1:21:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hearth and home"?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.22,1:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Libertus, come in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.46,1:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you? Are you all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.32,1:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.49,1:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way back to base now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.53,1:21:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need you to head to the junction{\i0}\N{\i1}in Section D.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.23,1:21:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're gonna join with another unit,{\i0}\N{\i1}make a clean sweep of the place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.53,1:21:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're one step away{\i0}\N{\i1}from realizing this revolution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.37,1:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's not let Pruvia's death be in vain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.67,1:21:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be waiting for you, hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.00,1:22:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't move until I say it's safe, all right?\N-I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.28,1:22:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulric, reporting.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.28,1:22:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.49,1:22:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.46,1:22:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-No!\N-Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.10,1:22:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some fight in you, Nyx,\NI'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.47,1:23:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Run. Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.01,1:23:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're still moving\Nwith that hollowpoint in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.31,1:23:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All Crowe could do was scream,\Nwhen one tore her insides apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.35,1:23:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why'd you do it?\N-Because the Kingsglaive is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.29,1:23:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man's battle fodder...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.09,1:23:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...sent to die in Insomnia's war...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.02,1:23:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...while our homes\Nare bound and shackled.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.63,1:23:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Niflheim took your home.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.76,1:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Took all our homes!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.67,1:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will ever change that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.04,1:23:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You never were too smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.51,1:23:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've had a new future\Nwith the empire.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.39,1:23:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to run, princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.70,1:24:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.07,1:24:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.72,1:24:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So many dead over so simple a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.79,1:24:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.57,1:24:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Power.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.50,1:24:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Untold power,\Nbeyond the control of someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.17,1:24:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Power....
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.88,1:25:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.63,1:25:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.60,1:25:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over. The daemons are unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.30,1:25:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucis is fallen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.91,1:25:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.38,1:25:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Plan on giving those kings\Na piece of your mind, princess?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.72,1:26:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a destiny to take care of here,\Nremember?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.29,1:26:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, didn't anyone tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.36,1:26:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the hero around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.41,1:26:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourselves, kings of Lucis.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.46,1:26:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You call upon the wards\Nof this world's future, mortal.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.73,1:26:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you come lusting for our power,\Nyou must first stand in our judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.83,1:26:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will you do nothing\Nwhilst Insomnia burns?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.90,1:26:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Old or new, or whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.47,1:26:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon your Wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.31,1:26:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not command us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.91,1:27:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is not even royal blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.38,1:27:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not fall to us to guard your city.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.58,1:27:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Man is a fool creature...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.29,1:27:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...clinging to his past\Nand cowering from his future.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.46,1:27:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasting his strength on bygone days.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.46,1:27:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what future are you wards of?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.40,1:27:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So shortsighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.80,1:27:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And cursed never to rise above it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.43,1:27:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.67,1:27:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have seen what this brave soul\Nis prepared to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.27,1:27:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He, too, seeks to safeguard the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.01,1:27:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.01,1:27:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, young king.\NWe will weigh your warrior's worth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.25,1:27:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But our boon does not come cheap.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.95,1:27:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The cost is a life. His or hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.42,1:27:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.46,1:27:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with your power.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.83,1:27:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.40,1:27:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came to tell you, you are no kings.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.27,1:28:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your worth has been weighed\Nand found wanting.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.34,1:28:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.31,1:28:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose your precious ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.72,1:28:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not too late to save it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.42,1:28:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to barter for your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.56,1:28:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.56,1:28:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.07,1:28:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving a future\Nto those who want to see it...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.31,1:28:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...is everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.91,1:28:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not fear,\Neven if that future is doomed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.58,1:28:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If that sentiment is not false,\Nperhaps you are worthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.08,1:28:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We will grant you our light.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.75,1:28:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But know it will set when the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.32,1:28:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And the price for it will be your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.76,1:29:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys drive a hard bargain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.47,1:29:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where do I sign?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.38,1:29:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.02,1:29:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyx....
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.42,1:29:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sorry.\N-Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.36,1:29:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.53,1:29:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.03,1:29:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For a change.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.83,1:29:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need another favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.50,1:29:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet Lunafreya Nox Fleuret,\Nour prince's beloved bride-to-be.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.81,1:29:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And she has the future of the world\Nin her hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.87,1:29:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep her safe, get her out of Insomnia.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.95,1:29:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot. You'll need this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.42,1:29:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Prince Noctis my regards.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.89,1:29:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Libertus will take care of you from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.12,1:30:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe journey, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.86,1:30:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-What will come of you?\N-What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.43,1:30:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Following the kings' orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.03,1:30:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will see the ring to Noctis.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.87,1:30:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The future will be safe. I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.48,1:30:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Planning on punching your way\Nout of the city? Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.95,1:30:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now we're even.\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.12,1:30:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle up\Nonce you're back in Galahd.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.79,1:30:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and everyone else\Nwill be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.56,1:30:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.13,1:30:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.02,1:31:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-Buckle up, princess.\N-My life is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.03,1:31:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the power of the Lucii returns.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.93,1:31:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter. You are out of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.80,1:31:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, I'll make some.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.70,1:31:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you hope to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.61,1:32:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,One man against an empire.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.68,1:32:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the daemons.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.75,1:32:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you save Insomnia\Nwith no wall to protect you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.18,1:32:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong.\NI'm not fighting to save Insomnia.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.24,1:33:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the might of the Old Wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.65,1:33:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Marvelous. Truly marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.25,1:35:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.69,1:35:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucis. Niflheim.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.06,1:35:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't who we fight for that matters,\Nonly what.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.73,1:35:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for our homes.\NThat is where our allegiance lies.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.21,1:36:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something you see every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.97,1:36:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, such a pitiable waste.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.34,1:36:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All those beautiful city streets,\Nall laid to unsightly ruin.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.31,1:37:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-I will return to Niflheim.\N-So soon?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.41,1:37:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The crystal is ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.98,1:37:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish this...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.42,1:37:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and see the daemons disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.12,1:37:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.29,1:37:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pitiable waste.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.10,1:37:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you serve the empire?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.14,1:37:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything they did?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.51,1:37:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not fault them\Nfor taking what was given.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.22,1:37:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I fault the man who gave it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.39,1:37:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who cowered behind his wall...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.52,1:37:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...and abandoned us\Nto save his throne and his son.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.09,1:37:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the ring,\Nand our homes will be free again.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.23,1:37:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The empire has promised it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.23,1:37:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see much of a future\Non the other side of that promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.30,1:38:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.07,1:38:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.14,1:38:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Give your dead sister peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.01,1:38:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you fight for if not that?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.06,1:38:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on. This could get bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.20,1:39:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Drautos.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.18,1:39:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.12,1:39:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Floor it!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.14,1:39:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Libertus!\N-Just keep your foot on the gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.36,1:40:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.33,1:40:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you, hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.80,1:40:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What of your kings' power now?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.63,1:40:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They've given you a burden\Nyou cannot hope to bear.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.80,1:40:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.74,1:40:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanting doesn't win wars.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.61,1:42:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For the honor of my home,\NI fought and killed under a king I loathed.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.36,1:42:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And still he betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.16,1:42:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He betrayed us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.33,1:42:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought for the same thing. All of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.40,1:42:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've looked too long on the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.37,1:42:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're blind to the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.64,1:42:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Predictable.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.21,1:42:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, I learn from history.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.38,1:42:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're a slave to the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.79,1:42:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A man's past is his pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.32,1:42:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.69,1:42:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My pride is shaping the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.94,1:43:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm gonna owe him big.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.29,1:43:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.56,1:43:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.47,1:43:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,King Regis did what he did for the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.65,1:43:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of him...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.45,1:43:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's still hope for our homes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.42,1:43:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope....
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.33,1:44:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the worst way to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.27,1:44:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rule well, young king.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.69,1:44:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We should move.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.26,1:44:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't safe here either.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.90,1:44:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.37,1:44:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about Nyx.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.60,1:44:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He can take care of himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.84,1:44:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.58,1:44:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.55,1:44:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We must part ways here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.35,1:44:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.36,1:45:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly travel in secrecy\Nalongside so great a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.89,1:45:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, too, have a promise to keep to Nyx.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.30,1:45:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray you two see each other again soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.54,1:45:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.87,1:45:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.48,1:45:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Libertus.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.46,1:45:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, queen!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.37,1:45:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You and the king\Nare always welcome in Galahd.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.70,1:45:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Nyx will be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.08,1:54:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been some while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.24,1:54:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you remember the last time{\i0}\N{\i1}you saw Lady Lunafreya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.08,1:54:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,About 12 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.62,1:54:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That would make you 8?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.62,1:54:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-You were kids.\N-Hope she hasn't gotten her hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.32,1:55:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? Calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.29,1:55:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and keep it together\Nwhen you meet her.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.39,1:55:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-She'll expect to see a fine, young prince.\N-Tell me something I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.36,1:55:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.90,1:55:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is your wedding\Nwe're talking about, Noc.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.57,1:55:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Knew that too.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.57,1:55:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You really gotta calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.67,1:55:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "Uh-oh"?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.34,1:55:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know.
